comment_data.body:
This seems to be faster as the result of the `c != 0x070f` comparison is used directly as the return value:
```suggestion
  if (c < 0x180b || c > 0xffff) {
    return c != 0x070f;
  }
```
~Also maybe it will be faster to remove the `c > 0xffff` check?~

